{"tid":2363136,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"愛國榴連bb慘遭食環署停牌14日","createTime":"2021-01-12T04:03:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T04:16:56.000Z","uid":94953,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bc3b3325c43634962c77bbdb024feb84aa9eb86b","tid":2363136,"uid":94953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:03:10.000Z","msg":"觀塘一食物製造廠經營者因無牌經營食肆，屢次違反《食物業規例》，被食物環境衞生署（食環署）署長暫時吊銷牌照十四天。<br />\n <br />\n該店鋪名為「DurianBB Limited」，位於觀塘敬業街65-67號敬運工業大廈2樓B室部分，由今日（一月八日）至一月二十一日須暫停營業。<br />\n <br />\n食環署發言人說：「有關店鋪經營者因上述違例事項，去年五月兩次被法庭定罪，共罰款四萬零六百元。本署亦根據違例記分制記下持牌人十五分，店鋪因此須停牌十四天。」<br />\n <br />\n有關持牌人亦因相同違例事項，去年一月兩次被法庭定罪，共罰款四萬零三百元，因而被記下十五分，店鋪去年十月被暫時吊銷牌照七天。<br />\n <br />\n發言人提醒食物業處所持牌人必須遵守《食物業規例》，否則牌照可能被暫時吊銷或取消。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NsxqCoZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNsxqCoZ.jpg&h=f7f96102&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n愛國都會有罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3443356e8bd4900d90f01d56546d1fa99748664","tid":2363136,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:03:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"950e4c1321686194bfa8861a6550c9792e8e4ee1","tid":2363136,"uid":384207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:06:10.000Z","msg":"支持警察,支持榴槤BB<br />\n咪就係衰在冇支持食環囉,衰左喇而家"},{"pid":"ff53dcc657b060640bfff20a3a52daedbbbd47fc","tid":2363136,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:08:38.000Z","msg":"點樣可以再舉報？"},{"pid":"545d4c9d3905d44446d0637d0fd348d6b62e40ad","tid":2363136,"uid":61604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:08:40.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"1fb34c7313a35c86744190ab